title: Holiday Jazz Music MP3 Collection #2 Rev1
description:
Holiday Jazz Music MP3 Collection #2 Rev1


Holiday cheer and warm wishes to you and yours.
These are some of my favorite jazz and pop christmas tunes carefully encoded using high variable bitrates.
All were sourced from 44/16 CDs, except Vince Guaraldi was from high resolution 96/24 source.
Give em a spin. All the songs will fit on a single CD-R.
Suggest you use ImgBurn -> ISO9660+Joliet -> Advanced -> Restrictions -> ISO9660 / Level 2 -> Joliet -> Level X
If your player has trouble with that, use settings with more restrictions.
